{% extends "page.html.twig" %}

{% block title %}Gutter Cleaning in Metro Vancouver BC | Clean Gutters Crew{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
    <section class="gutter-section">

        <h1>1. Gutter Cleaning</h1>

        <img style="width: 100%" src="/assets/images/services/Gutters.png">
        
        <h2>Why It Is Critical</h2>

        <p>
            Your gutters are your home’s drainage system. When they are clogged with leaves, pine needles, and debris,
            water stops flowing properly and begins looking for a way inside your home’s structure.
            In a rainy climate like British Columbia, this becomes especially dangerous.
        </p>

        <p>Clogged gutters:</p>

        <ul>
            <li>Cause roof leaks</li>
            <li>Damage fascia and soffits</li>
            <li>Saturate foundation walls</li>
            <li>Lead to basement moisture</li>
            <li>Create ideal conditions for mold</li>
        </ul>

        <p>
            Regular gutter cleaning is not cosmetic maintenance — it is structural protection.
        </p>

        <h2>Risks You Prevent</h2>

        <ul>
            <li>Roof leaks</li>
            <li>Foundation damage</li>
            <li>Basement mold</li>
            <li>Ice buildup in winter</li>
            <li>Siding deterioration</li>
            <li>Pest infestations</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Financial Impact</h2>

        <p>The cost of maintenance is a fraction of:</p>

        <ul>
            <li>Roof replacement</li>
            <li>Mold remediation</li>
            <li>Insulation repair</li>
            <li>Structural foundation repairs</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Psychological Benefit</h2>

        <p>During heavy rainstorms, you feel calm.</p>
        <p>No anxiety about hidden leaks.</p>
        <p>No fear of unexpected repair bills.</p>

        <h2>Table</h2>

        <div class="table-wrapper">
            <table class="gutter-table">
                <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>If Ignored</th>
                    <th>What Happens</th>
                    <th>Regular Cleaning Provides</th>
                </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td>Debris accumulates</td>
                    <td>Water overflows</td>
                    <td>Controlled drainage</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Standing water</td>
                    <td>Wood rot</td>
                    <td>Protection for fascia &amp; soffits</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Winter freezing</td>
                    <td>Gutter deformation</td>
                    <td>Longer system lifespan</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Water near foundation</td>
                    <td>Cracks &amp; damp basement</td>
                    <td>Structural protection</td>
                </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>

    </section>
{% endblock %}

{% block styles %}
    <style>
        .gutter-section {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            background: #ffffff;
            line-height: 1.7;
            font-family: Inter, sans-serif;
        }

        .gutter-section h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .gutter-section h2 {
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-top: 35px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .gutter-section ul {
            padding-left: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .gutter-section li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .table-wrapper {
            overflow-x: auto;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .gutter-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            min-width: 600px;
        }

        .gutter-table thead {
            background: #f4f6f8;
        }

        .gutter-table th,
        .gutter-table td {
            padding: 14px 16px;
            text-align: left;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }

        .gutter-table th {
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .gutter-table tbody tr:hover {
            background: #fafafa;
        }

        /* Mobile */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .gutter-section {
                padding: 25px 15px;
            }

            .gutter-section h1 {
                font-size: 22px;
            }

            .gutter-section h2 {
                font-size: 18px;
            }
        }
    </style>
{% endblock %}